CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946 reads: "Newlyweds - Miss Pauline King, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. J.W. King of Broad Street was united in marriage to Robert R. Williams at the home of the Kings early in July. A few close friends and relatives were in attendance. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Full length group portrait of groom Robert R. William, and bride Pauline King Williams wearing two piece dress, standing in interior with patterned wallpaper
